{"tid":361700,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"700 2017中期業績總結，最新PE和明天股價預測","createTime":"2017-08-16T10:43:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-16T13:43:18.000Z","uid":77625,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"acc5ef46a4c12c04597b6afdad07821e173fa9a2","tid":361700,"uid":77625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T10:43:49.000Z","msg":"一張圖睇曬，紅色highlight係今日業績，其他係大行之前估<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/16/183647_a6f5cb2be10d5cb8da1f2cf65e2cc32e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F16%2F183647_a6f5cb2be10d5cb8da1f2cf65e2cc32e.png&h=8355bdaf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n總結<br />\n<br />\n1. Earning attributable to shareholder 升70% 真係好恐怖，特別係咁大隻<br />\n<br />\n2. 手遊revenue過左PC game<br />\n<br />\n3. 廣告個邊雖然佔收入%同之前一樣，但係呢季有王者係手遊個邊，keep 到same %即係話廣告收入都做得好好，但WeChat 廣告仲係低過news同video既廣告錢，呢到好多potential<br />\n<br />\n4.今日有新game出,千萬人封測<br />\n<br />\n5. 700投資China Unicom,有睇歷史都知佢一直都好想進軍電信商，預期同WeChat會多D合作"},{"pid":"cb637364daf09353322ad45a922d0bf8e06c353b","tid":361700,"uid":77625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T10:44:52.000Z","msg":"唔知聽日有無7%<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有就係345蚊!"},{"pid":"1c52d3cdc663a051c5aea5e5e55b8ef22e01507f","tid":361700,"uid":9844,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T10:45:34.000Z","msg":"三萬億市值既企鵝仲可以做到同比增70%太強<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"464440276305bf406ce2fc842865cb4252451a7a","tid":361700,"uid":77625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T10:46:10.000Z","msg":"期指升左100幾點，點都有10蚊"},{"pid":"869d758bbd655f552f7f54932051087d747eec98","tid":361700,"uid":77625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T10:46:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>三萬億市值既企鵝仲可以做到同比增70%太強<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></bl